<section>
<h2>How to implement</h2>
<h3>Open overlay</h3>
<pre>
	<code>&lt;button  data-wb-doaction='{ &quot;action&quot;: &quot;open&quot;, &quot;source&quot;: &quot;#mid-screen&quot; }' class=&quot;wb-bubble&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;image/default-avatar.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/button&gt;
	</code>
</pre>
<p>Where:</p>
<dl class="dl-horizontal">
<dt><code>&quot;action&quot;: &quot;open&quot;</code></dt>
<dd>Will open an overlay by using the overlay plugin.</dd>
<dt><code>&quot;source&quot;: #mid-screen</code></dt>
<dd>The source represent a pointer to section id, which will be included in the overlay panel</dd>

</dl>
